Sta ti mislis?

9
00:03:38,835 --> 00:03:40,404
Oh, ne znam.

10
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:43,165
Jos uvek mi se dopada
ova haljina.

11
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:45,959
Pa, majko, nije vazno
sta se nama dopada.

12
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:49,599
Pitanje je...

13
00:03:49,799 --> 00:03:52,680
Sta bi zeleo Silas?

14
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:58,125
Silas!
Nesto je u bazenu!

15
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,924
Ovo je bila pesma
"Angel Eyes",

16
00:03:59,959 --> 00:04:04,039
a vi slusate WQQG
u Wilmington-u, Kentucky.

17
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,765
Kada se vratimo,
razgovaracemo o...

18
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,359
Hej! Sta, do djavola,
nije u redu sa tobom?

19
00:04:08,394 --> 00:04:11,240
Zar me nisi cuo?
Imamo nesto u bazenu.

20
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,479
Zasto si, do djavola,
to uradio?

21
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,844
Nije bio mrtav.

22
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:21,759
Pa, vadi ga odatle. Hocu
da ovaj bazen bude cist.

23
00:04:22,479 --> 00:04:25,319
Mora da trazim previse.
Trazim li previse?

24
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,559
Hej!
Hej, glupane!

25
00:04:28,594 --> 00:04:30,239
Trazim li previse?

26
00:04:30,274 --> 00:04:31,399
Da.

27
00:04:36,719 --> 00:04:39,599
Morao sam da preklinjem nedeljama
da bih ti nasao taj posao.

28
00:04:39,918 --> 00:04:42,759
Nagovorio sam ga da ti da zubarsko
osiguranje koje pokriva celu porodicu.

29
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:46,279
Kako ces sada da pokrijes
kompletno porodicno osiguranje?

30
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:49,638
Silas, moras da budes
mnogo pouzdaniji.

31
00:04:49,673 --> 00:04:52,119
Zenis se mojom malom necakom.

32
00:04:52,154 --> 00:04:53,923
Pridruzujes se nasoj porodici.

33
00:04:53,958 --> 00:04:56,839
Znam da si pristojan momak,
negde u dubini duse,

34
00:04:57,239 --> 00:05:00,119
ali moras da se zapitas,
sta svi mi vidimo spolja?

35
00:05:02,678 --> 00:05:05,239
Poradicemo na tome.

36
00:05:05,274 --> 00:05:07,798
Jesi li kupio prsten?

37
00:05:08,358 --> 00:05:11,239
Vidis sad', to je onaj deo
biti pouzdaniji,

38
00:05:11,479 --> 00:05:13,398
o kome smo razgovarali
malopre.

39
00:05:13,433 --> 00:05:15,399
Ona ima prsten.

40
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:17,043
A ti si joj ga kupio,
zar ne?

41
00:05:17,078 --> 00:05:19,599
Pretpostavljam da ga nije
kupila sama sebi.

42
00:05:25,479 --> 00:05:28,358
Nijagarini vodopadi!

43
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:32,078
Pogledaj kako su veliki.
Ogromni su!

44
00:05:32,558 --> 00:05:35,243
Jeste li znali da 6 miliona
kubnih stopa vode

45
00:05:35,278 --> 00:05:38,958
pada preko ivice u svakoj minuti,
170 stopa nize?

46
00:05:39,798 --> 00:05:41,003
Jeste li znali to?

47
00:05:41,038 --> 00:05:43,918
Pise u brosuri, ako
zelis da bacis pogled.

48
00:05:45,118 --> 00:05:47,683
Cammy?

49
00:05:47,718 --> 00:05:48,998
Zasto i dalje radis ovo?

50
00:05:49,033 --> 00:05:50,243
Zato, Raymond-e, sto treba
da znas

51
00:05:50,278 --> 00:05:52,838
da su Nijagarini vodopadi
mesto za ljubavnike.

52
00:05:52,873 --> 00:05:54,923
Mislim, to je slogan.

53
00:05:54,958 --> 00:05:57,398
Da, odstampan je bas tu,
na brosuri.

54
00:05:57,433 --> 00:06:00,003
Vidis?

55
00:06:00,038 --> 00:06:02,203
Sranje, Raymond-e.

56
00:06:02,238 --> 00:06:05,118
Mislim da je Silas odsluzio
svoj dug drustvu.

57
00:06:08,037 --> 00:06:10,118
Draga, on je na uslovnoj.
Ne sme da napusti drzavu.

58
00:06:10,153 --> 00:06:12,997
Pa, ko kaze?
- Drzava. Takav je zakon.

59
00:06:13,718 --> 00:06:15,998
Pa, onda neka to bude
nasa mala tajna.

60
00:06:16,033 --> 00:06:18,443
I jos je zabavnije
na taj nacin.

61
00:06:18,478 --> 00:06:21,357
Na Nijagarine vodopade ljudi
idu kada su zaljubljeni.

62
00:06:22,157 --> 00:06:24,838
To je pravi zakon...

63
00:06:24,873 --> 00:06:26,202
Zakon ljubavi.

64
00:06:26,237 --> 00:06:29,118
Oh, draga, izgledas prelepo.

65
00:06:31,717 --> 00:06:34,598
Zelim da zapamtim danasnji
dan, bas onakav kakav bude,

66
00:06:35,597 --> 00:06:38,438
onako kako izgledam,
onako kako osecam.

67
00:06:39,597 --> 00:06:42,477
Zelim da uvek bude
ovako dobro.

68
00:06:42,757 --> 00:06:43,758
Osmeh.

69
00:06:47,557 --> 00:06:50,437
Pitam se kako se Silas
oseca.

70
00:06:54,277 --> 00:06:57,157
Silas, nemoj da zajebes ovo.

71
00:07:00,397 --> 00:07:03,237
Srecni. Srecni.
Svi su srecni.

72
00:07:36,036 --> 00:07:38,917
Draga!
Volim te!

73
00:07:41,636 --> 00:07:44,816
Da li ti, Silas,
uzimas ovu zenu, Camille,

74
00:07:45,676 --> 00:07:49,700
da ti bude zakonita zena, da
je volis i postujes, u bolesti i u
zdravlju,

75
00:07:50,756 --> 00:07:54,300
u svetom braku ljubavi,
dok vas smrt ne rastavi?

76
00:08:02,796 --> 00:08:05,636
Tvoj je red, Tigre.
Mozes ti to.

77
00:08:09,996 --> 00:08:12,036
Hoces li da ponovim
pitanje, sine?

78
00:08:12,071 --> 00:08:14,756
Samo reci da, duso.

79
00:08:14,791 --> 00:08:16,281
Reci da.

80
00:08:16,316 --> 00:08:18,756
Samo reci da.

81
00:08:18,791 --> 00:08:20,800
Da.

82
00:08:20,835 --> 00:08:22,716
Da.
- Da.

83
00:08:37,516 --> 00:08:40,135
Oh, cekaj!

84
00:08:44,555 --> 00:08:46,796
Oh, Isuse... Pirinac.

85
00:08:46,831 --> 00:08:49,000
Zaboravila sam da uzmem
pirinac.

86
00:08:49,035 --> 00:08:51,361
Moramo da bacimo pirinac.
Pirinac je za srecu.

87
00:08:51,396 --> 00:08:54,275
Cammy... U redu je.
- Pa zar niko nije doneo pirinac?

88
00:08:54,755 --> 00:08:56,636
Duso, u redu je.
- U redu je.

89
00:09:20,355 --> 00:09:23,235
Cestitam, Silas.

90
00:09:23,835 --> 00:09:26,715
Ne pleses sa svojom
lepom nevestom?

91
00:09:26,955 --> 00:09:28,440
Ne umem da plesem.

92
00:09:28,475 --> 00:09:31,355
Pa, ovo je tvoja noc
vencanja, sine.

93
00:09:31,595 --> 00:09:34,474
Nikoga nece biti briga
kako izgledas.

94
00:09:34,715 --> 00:09:37,155
Ne mogu da plesem
sa njom.

95
00:09:37,195 --> 00:09:39,399
To je zbog Camille.

96
00:09:39,434 --> 00:09:41,515
Ponekad samo osecam
kao da...

97
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:43,120
Kao da imas sumnje.

98
00:09:43,155 --> 00:09:46,035
Kao da hocu da je udarim!
- Dobri Gospode!

99
00:09:46,795 --> 00:09:49,675
Ma sta kazete. Mislim,
ta devojka moze da prica.

100
00:09:50,115 --> 00:09:52,994
Sve sto radi to je da prica.
Prica, prica, prica, prica!

101
00:09:53,554 --> 00:09:58,100
Ali upravo si je ozenio.
- Svestenice... Porazgovarao bih sa
Silas-om.

102
00:10:00,155 --> 00:10:03,034
Ma sta kazes.

103
00:10:06,874 --> 00:10:08,439
Ti si srecan covek, Silas.

104
00:10:08,474 --> 00:10:11,354
Decko, ta devojka bi ucinila
skoro sve za tebe.

105
00:10:11,394 --> 00:10:14,275
Silas!
Dolazi ovamo, Tigre!

106
00:10:14,755 --> 00:10:17,634
Osim, mozda da zaveze.

107
00:10:26,994 --> 00:10:29,874
Znas...

108
00:10:30,274 --> 00:10:32,674
U svakom braku postoje
problemi tokom prve godine.

109
00:10:32,714 --> 00:10:35,114
Tvoji su samo poceli u
prvih nekoliko casova.

110
00:10:35,149 --> 00:10:37,514
Znam da ces raditi na
tome da ih resis,

111
00:10:37,549 --> 00:10:39,394
zato sto...

112
00:10:39,434 --> 00:10:42,274
Pa, ako ih ne resis, moracu
da vratim nazad u zatvor.

113
00:10:42,314 --> 00:10:45,194
Tri prekrsaja, i neces
nikada izaci odatle.

114
00:10:45,674 --> 00:10:48,554
Hajde, Silas.
Hajde.

115
00:10:53,514 --> 00:10:56,319
Motor sa prikolicom!
- Sta je, do djavola, to?

116
00:10:56,354 --> 00:10:59,234
A evo nesto i za put na
Nijagarine vodopade.

117
00:10:59,634 --> 00:11:01,394
Za tebe i sve tvoje slike.

118
00:11:01,429 --> 00:11:03,439
Hvala ti, ujka Raymond-e.

119
00:11:03,474 --> 00:11:06,353
Hvala za motor. Ti si
najbolji. Volim te.

120
00:11:08,794 --> 00:11:13,673
Zdravo svima!
- Zapamti, budi dobra. Oboje.

121
00:11:13,674 --> 00:11:15,039
Osmeh, svi!

122
00:11:15,074 --> 00:11:17,954
Sa tobom je moja mala
necaka. Budi dobar.

123
00:11:20,033 --> 00:11:22,894
Cuvaj je, Silas.
- Do vidjenja!

124
00:11:22,929 --> 00:11:27,000
Do vidjenja, okrutni svete!
Zdravo! - Zdravo, draga!

125
00:11:50,433 --> 00:11:53,313
Nijagarini vodopadi!

126
00:11:56,793 --> 00:11:58,918
Nijagarini vodopadi,
mi dolazimo!

127
00:11:58,953 --> 00:12:03,210
Jesi li video moju knjigu?
"Napravite savrsen medeni mesec"!

128
00:12:12,073 --> 00:12:14,953
Ovo se ne vidja svaki dan.

129
00:12:20,672 --> 00:12:22,278
Gde vam je kupatilo?

130
00:12:22,313 --> 00:12:23,918
Na putu smo jos od
Covington-a.

131
00:12:23,953 --> 00:12:26,833
Rekla sam Silas-u da devojka
ne moze da izdrzi vecno.

132
00:12:47,552 --> 00:12:49,592
Imas macu na glavi,
covece.

133
00:12:49,627 --> 00:12:52,472
Imas malu macu.

134
00:12:52,872 --> 00:12:55,712
Ali ozbiljno, dobar motor,
druze.

135
00:13:05,032 --> 00:13:07,912
Zelis li zagrejanu, kauboju?
- Pogledaj tamo.

136
00:13:08,312 --> 00:13:09,917
Zar nisu lepa stvorenja?

137
00:13:09,952 --> 00:13:14,250
Znas, kad smo kod konja,
ja sam neka vrsta filozofa.

138
00:13:16,032 --> 00:13:18,912
Pretpostavljam da se pitas,
sta sam mislio sa tim.

139
00:13:22,872 --> 00:13:25,752
Hej, Tigre, ovamo!
Imamo drustvo!

140
00:13:28,032 --> 00:13:29,471
Vidi.

141
00:13:29,511 --> 00:13:31,272
Silas je dobio veliko
skracenje kazne

142
00:13:31,307 --> 00:13:32,717
zato sto je pokazao tako
dobro ponasanje.

143
00:13:32,752 --> 00:13:35,272
Mislim, tako je Raymond rekao,
dobro ponasanje. To je istina.

144
00:13:35,307 --> 00:13:37,632
Ne pricaj im to.
- Ali to je istina!

145
00:13:37,667 --> 00:13:39,076
Nije me sramota da
im ispricam.

146
00:13:39,111 --> 00:13:41,412
- Camille... - To samo pokazuje
kako si moderan.

147
00:13:41,447 --> 00:13:43,711
Odsluzio si svoje i
sada si moj.

148
00:13:43,746 --> 00:13:45,917
Isla sam mu u posete.

149
00:13:45,952 --> 00:13:48,351
Izgledao je tako slatko u
narandzastom odelu.

150
00:13:48,386 --> 00:13:50,949
Svi cuvari su rekli
da smo savrsen par.

151
00:13:50,984 --> 00:13:53,511
Poznajem Silas-a od svoje
seste godine.

152
00:13:53,546 --> 00:13:55,872
Pokazi im svoje tetovaze, Tigre.
- Ne!

153
00:13:55,907 --> 00:13:58,751
Tada ih nije imao.

154
00:13:59,431 --> 00:14:03,910
On je takav buntovnik, zar ne?
Mislim, niko vise ne pusi.

155
00:14:08,671 --> 00:14:12,350
Jesu li kamiondzije stvarno
ovoliko fine, ili smo mi samo
dobro raspolozeni?

156
00:14:17,071 --> 00:14:19,831
Morala si da im ispricas
bas sve.

157
00:14:19,866 --> 00:14:22,431
Mislim da me haljina odala.

158
00:14:22,471 --> 00:14:24,671
Osim toga, pravilo br.15, u
prirucniku za mladence, kaze:

159
00:14:24,706 --> 00:14:27,231
"Uvek ispricajte ljudima
da ste tek vencani.

160
00:14:27,271 --> 00:14:29,716
Ponekad ce vam ponuditi
specijalan popust".

161
00:14:29,751 --> 00:14:32,631
Zasto ih ne pozoves da idu sa
nama? - Nemoj da se duris, Tigre.

162
00:14:34,191 --> 00:14:37,071
Ja se "ne durim, Tigre".
Ja sam besan.

163
00:14:37,351 --> 00:14:39,711
Zasto moras da budes tako
prokleto srecna, sve vreme?

164
00:14:39,751 --> 00:14:42,036
Cini da oboje izgledamo
glupo.

165
00:14:42,071 --> 00:14:44,951
Znas, muka mi je od tvojih
prokletih prirucnika za mladence,

166
00:14:45,551 --> 00:14:48,430
tvojih prica o Nijagarinim
vodopadima i od sveg tvog
pricanja.

167
00:14:49,351 --> 00:14:51,356
Sve sto radis to je
da pricas!

168
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:53,350
Zar ne mozes malo da
zavezes u zivotu?

169
00:14:53,385 --> 00:14:55,871
Molim te.
Molim te.

170
00:14:55,911 --> 00:14:58,671
Samo pokusaj i drzi usta
zatvorena, bar jednom.

171
00:14:58,706 --> 00:15:01,550
Molim te.

172
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:05,471
Mozes li to?

173
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:20,150
Ne cini to.

174
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:23,431
Imaju marihuanu.

175
00:15:28,231 --> 00:15:31,110
Nikada ranije nisam probala
marihuanu.

176
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:34,550
Molim te.

177
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:39,390
Zavezi.

178
00:15:43,230 --> 00:15:46,110
Jesi li ti nekada probao
marihuanu?

179
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:01,434
Gospodjo?

180
00:16:01,469 --> 00:16:03,470
Jeste li u redu?

181
00:16:03,505 --> 00:16:05,834
Da.

182
00:16:05,869 --> 00:16:08,750
Kada stignemo do vodopada,
bicemo u redu.

183
00:16:09,310 --> 00:16:12,189
Oboje jedva cekamo da
stignemo tamo.

184
00:16:14,789 --> 00:16:17,630
Samo, Silas je jak i
cutljiv tip,

185
00:16:18,110 --> 00:16:20,109
a ja nekada govorim vise
nego sto je on navikao,

186
00:16:20,144 --> 00:16:21,909
ali mu ne smeta, stvarno.

187
00:16:26,189 --> 00:16:28,754
Vidis?

188
00:16:28,789 --> 00:16:31,669
Jedva ceka da stigne tamo.

189
00:16:58,229 --> 00:17:01,108
Prica, prica, prica,
prica, prica!

190
00:17:01,829 --> 00:17:04,634
Prica!

191
00:17:04,669 --> 00:17:07,549
Prica, prica...!

192
00:17:21,909 --> 00:17:24,788
Konj ce se uplasiti od
najmanje stvari -

193
00:17:24,868 --> 00:17:26,994
procvetalog zbuna,
barice vode.

194
00:17:27,029 --> 00:17:29,908
On vidi baricu, ali je
ne razume.

195
00:17:29,948 --> 00:17:32,828
Pa se propinje, uplasen.

196
00:17:33,468 --> 00:17:36,349
Dakle...
Hvala.

197
00:17:37,149 --> 00:17:40,028
Dakle, mi ljudi, mi je
vidimo kakva jeste.

198
00:17:40,428 --> 00:17:42,108
To je samo voda.

199
00:17:42,148 --> 00:17:44,988
Pa zasto bi bili uplaseni?

200
00:17:45,188 --> 00:17:47,673
Pratite li me,
gospodjo?

201
00:17:47,708 --> 00:17:50,589
Zao mi je.
Nesto o konjima...?

202
00:17:50,789 --> 00:17:52,033
Da, gospodjo.

203
00:17:52,068 --> 00:17:54,748
Samo nesto o konjima.

204
00:17:59,228 --> 00:18:01,433
Pa onda, pretpostavljam
da je to sve.

205
00:18:01,468 --> 00:18:04,348
Hvala na drustvu,
gosp. Cowboy Bob.

206
00:18:04,508 --> 00:18:07,388
Hej... Uspecete vas dvoje.

207
00:18:08,388 --> 00:18:12,290
Imam takav osecaj. Imate
taj osecaj povezanosti.

208
00:18:13,908 --> 00:18:15,353
Dobro.

209
00:18:15,388 --> 00:18:17,948
Do vidjenja, gospodjo.

210
00:18:17,983 --> 00:18:20,828
Zdravo.

211
00:18:21,188 --> 00:18:24,067
Da.

212
00:18:33,147 --> 00:18:34,673
Hajde.

213
00:18:34,708 --> 00:18:37,587
Ne smemo da propustimo
te proklete vodopade.

214
00:18:43,667 --> 00:18:46,148
Silas, da li me volis?

215
00:18:46,183 --> 00:18:48,627
Ozenio sam te, zar ne?

216
00:18:48,662 --> 00:18:51,227
Tigre, molim te.

217
00:18:51,267 --> 00:18:54,107
Ti me volis, zar ne?

218
00:19:08,747 --> 00:19:11,627
To stvarno nije bilo pitanje koje
sam nameravala da ti postavim.

219
00:19:13,107 --> 00:19:15,987
Znas, samo je ispalo
nekako pogresno.

220
00:19:19,067 --> 00:19:21,947
Nisam mislila... Ne mislim
"ljubav", "volis me".

221
00:19:22,547 --> 00:19:24,112
Pa, ne jos, u svakom
slucaju.

222
00:19:24,147 --> 00:19:26,747
Mislim, ljudi vremenom zavole
jedno drugo, tako da imamo
dosta vremena.

223
00:19:26,782 --> 00:19:27,831
Camille!

224
00:19:27,866 --> 00:19:30,747
Popni se na motor,
molim te.

225
00:19:34,107 --> 00:19:36,986
Molim te popni se na
motor!

226
00:20:50,546 --> 00:20:52,646
Silas, moj prsten!

227
00:20:52,681 --> 00:20:54,746
Ispustila sam prsten!

228
00:20:59,666 --> 00:21:02,546
Silas!

229
00:22:43,624 --> 00:22:46,504
Nemoj da sedis toliko blizu
novog TV-a. Oslepeces.

230
00:22:47,384 --> 00:22:49,749
Izvoli.

231
00:22:49,784 --> 00:22:52,664
Izgleda da je tatica opet
zaboravio svoj novcanik.

232
00:23:00,864 --> 00:23:02,229
Telefon!

233
00:23:02,264 --> 00:23:05,144
Ti, ti si prekriven...
- Telefon! Treba mi telefon!

234
00:23:10,104 --> 00:23:12,984
Koga zove?
- Ne znam.

235
00:23:14,424 --> 00:23:16,824
9-1-1. Kako mogu da
vam pomognem?

236
00:23:16,859 --> 00:23:19,704
Halo?
Halo?

237
00:23:20,744 --> 00:23:23,583
Molim vas, nemojte nas
povrediti. Mi nemamo nista.

238
00:23:23,618 --> 00:23:26,464
Ubio sam je!

239
00:23:29,184 --> 00:23:32,063
Nije me briga sta si uradio,
OK? - Ubio sam je!

240
00:23:32,098 --> 00:23:34,944
Necemo reci nikome nista.
- Ubio sam je!

241
00:23:35,544 --> 00:23:38,423
Samo idi. Samo...

242
00:23:43,103 --> 00:23:45,983
Evo... Samo uzmi novac. Molim
te nemoj nas povrediti.

243
00:24:16,943 --> 00:24:19,823
Camille!

244
00:24:31,582 --> 00:24:34,463
Camille!

245
00:24:38,423 --> 00:24:41,302
Camille?

246
00:24:41,422 --> 00:24:44,303
Camille!

247
00:24:45,502 --> 00:24:48,383
Oh, tu si, Tigre!

248
00:24:58,783 --> 00:25:00,267
Jesi li dobro?

249
00:25:00,302 --> 00:25:02,863
Da. Ovde sam.

250
00:25:02,898 --> 00:25:05,387
Malo sam blatnjava.

251
00:25:05,422 --> 00:25:08,303
Mislim da necu moci da
vratim haljinu.

252
00:25:09,302 --> 00:25:12,183
Vrat mi je malo povredjen,
ali mozes da ga dotaknes.

253
00:25:19,502 --> 00:25:22,083
Mislio sam da sam te ubio.

254
00:25:22,117 --> 00:25:24,662
Tigre, pogledaj svoju kosulju!

255
00:25:24,697 --> 00:25:27,307
Izgledas uzasno.

256
00:25:27,342 --> 00:25:30,222
Moracu da te odvedem
doktoru.

257
00:25:31,501 --> 00:25:34,382
Sta se desilo?

258
00:25:34,462 --> 00:25:37,307
Imali smo udes.

259
00:25:37,342 --> 00:25:40,202
Ne secam se mnogo.
Ja samo...

260
00:25:40,237 --> 00:25:43,062
Tigre, treses se.
Jesi li dobro?

261
00:25:44,102 --> 00:25:46,922
Mislio sam da te vise nema.

262
00:25:46,957 --> 00:25:49,741
Ne idem ja nigde.

263
00:25:50,421 --> 00:25:53,302
Osim na Nijagarine vodopade
sa tobom.

264
00:26:05,261 --> 00:26:08,141
Jesi li sigurna da se ne
secas nicega?

265
00:26:08,861 --> 00:26:11,742
Pa, secam se vencanja i
da sam se popela na motor.

266
00:26:13,341 --> 00:26:16,222
Jesmo li se zaustavljali negde?
Taj deo mi je malo nejasan.

267
00:26:17,461 --> 00:26:20,341
Oh, u pravi si. Ovde.

268
00:26:21,462 --> 00:26:24,341
Oh, Tigre, nasao si ga.

269
00:26:25,461 --> 00:26:28,341
Oh, Tigre, tvoj jadni motor.

270
00:26:28,981 --> 00:26:31,381
Treba li da odemo u onu kucu?
Mozda ce nam dati prevoz.

271
00:26:31,416 --> 00:26:34,261
Ne. To je losa ideja.
Farmeri.

272
00:26:35,622 --> 00:26:37,981
Tigre. Hej!
- Camille! Sagni se!

273
00:26:40,541 --> 00:26:42,781
Nisu cak ni dali znak sirenom,
Tigre!

274
00:26:42,816 --> 00:26:44,945
Ja sam na uslovnoj!

275
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:47,861
Oh, Camille!
Umalo sam uprskala!

276
00:26:55,981 --> 00:26:58,860
Zdravo.

277
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:20,946
Je li rekao koga je zvao?

278
00:27:20,981 --> 00:27:23,800
Ne. Ustvari nisakim nije
razgovarao.

279
00:27:23,835 --> 00:27:26,620
Rekao je...
Rekao je da je ubio.

280
00:27:27,100 --> 00:27:29,981
I izgledao je stvarno
potreseno zbog toga.

281
00:27:32,950 --> 00:27:36,500
I nosio je smoking, sto mi
je izgledalo cudno.

282
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:41,100
Je li rekao koga je ubio?
- Ubio je nas prokleti TV.

283
00:27:41,940 --> 00:27:44,820
To smo vec ustanovili, sine.

284
00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:52,345
Serife!
Imamo ovo.

285
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:55,260
Proveri ih. Vidi sta cemo
da dobijemo.

286
00:28:08,579 --> 00:28:11,460
Hej, Camille!
Jesi li u redu?

287
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:14,900
Cujes li me? Camille?
- Izlazim za minut!

288
00:28:23,019 --> 00:28:25,900
Raymond...
- Silas?

289
00:28:26,899 --> 00:28:29,745
Silas, sta se desava?

290
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:32,659
Nesto nije u redu sa Camille.
- Jel' ona dobro?

291
00:28:33,179 --> 00:28:35,504
Pa, da, kaze da jeste.

292
00:28:35,539 --> 00:28:38,420
Zeli da nastavi dalje, ali...
Nesto nije u redu.

293
00:28:39,940 --> 00:28:41,264
Ne sada.

294
00:28:41,299 --> 00:28:44,180
Imate poziv od nekog serifa u
Ohaju koji istrazuje pljacku.

295
00:28:44,659 --> 00:28:47,379
Kaze da mora da razgovara sa
vama brzo. - U redu, u redu.
Silas, slusaj.

296
00:28:47,414 --> 00:28:48,145
Hocu da razgovaras
sa njom,

297
00:28:48,180 --> 00:28:51,059
reci Camille, ako je bolesna,
okreni se i vrati kuci.

298
00:28:51,379 --> 00:28:54,259
Imace ceo zivot da vidi
vodopade. Hoces li joj reci to?

299
00:28:54,379 --> 00:28:57,259
Sacekaj malo.

300
00:29:00,779 --> 00:29:03,659
Da, Foster.

301
00:29:04,739 --> 00:29:07,618
Sta?

302
00:29:08,259 --> 00:29:11,139
Dolazim u krevet, Tigre!

303
00:29:29,739 --> 00:29:33,119
Posle toplog tusiranja,
ja sam vesela maca.

304
00:29:37,419 --> 00:29:40,018
Odlucila sam da nema
vise durenja za Camille.

305
00:29:40,053 --> 00:29:42,224
Potrebno je dvoje za tango.

306
00:29:42,259 --> 00:29:45,138
Napravicu ovo zabavnim
i za tebe.

307
00:29:46,418 --> 00:29:49,298
Dodji...

308
00:29:49,858 --> 00:29:52,739
Dodji kod mene...

309
00:29:56,578 --> 00:29:59,458
Tigre?

310
00:30:00,218 --> 00:30:03,098
Tigre.

311
00:31:03,217 --> 00:31:06,098
Dobro jutro. Ovo je vas
poziv za budjenje.

312
00:31:15,618 --> 00:31:18,497
Camille?

313
00:31:19,657 --> 00:31:22,537
Budi se...

314
00:31:23,417 --> 00:31:26,297
Vreme za budjenje.

315
00:31:35,377 --> 00:31:38,257
Camille!

316
00:31:45,217 --> 00:31:48,097
Tigre...

317
00:31:49,296 --> 00:31:52,177
Sanjala sam nesto.

318
00:31:59,376 --> 00:32:01,542
Vidi ti njega.
Sav skockan.

319
00:32:01,577 --> 00:32:04,457
Da.
- U cemu je stvar, sreco?

320
00:32:06,737 --> 00:32:09,617
Hocu li dobiti poljubac
ovog jutra?

321
00:32:15,577 --> 00:32:17,861
To je bilo rukovanje,
ne poljubac.

322
00:32:17,896 --> 00:32:20,777
Treba da se istusiram.
- Ali, obucen si.

323
00:32:21,296 --> 00:32:24,177
Znam.

324
00:32:36,496 --> 00:32:38,381
Znas, uvek kada se nadjem na
nekom novom mestu, kao ovom,

325
00:32:38,416 --> 00:32:40,976
uvek mislim, kako bi bilo ziveti
ovde umesto kuci, znas?

326
00:32:41,011 --> 00:32:42,861
Mislim, sta da uvek zivim ovde?

327
00:32:42,896 --> 00:32:45,296
A onda pomislim da nikada
ne bih upoznala Silas-a.

328
00:32:45,331 --> 00:32:47,661
Sta da si ti ziveo na drugom
mestu i da se nismo upoznali?

329
00:32:47,696 --> 00:32:50,576
Onda pomislim, upoznala bih te gde
god zivela. To je predodredjeno.

330
00:32:57,296 --> 00:33:00,176
Ljubav je mocna stvar,
Silas.

331
00:33:00,816 --> 00:33:03,696
To je stvar koja me pokrece.

332
00:33:10,296 --> 00:33:13,176
Dobro bi mi doslo
malo boje.

333
00:33:14,336 --> 00:33:17,215
Izgledas...
Lepo.

334
00:33:19,296 --> 00:33:21,460
Stvarno?
- Da.

335
00:33:21,495 --> 00:33:24,376
Slusaj, hoces li da probas jos?
Kupicu ti koliko god hoces.

336
00:33:51,535 --> 00:33:54,415
Mogu li da dobijem i
taj sesir, molim vas?

337
00:33:56,135 --> 00:33:59,015
To ce biti $959.29.

338
00:34:00,215 --> 00:34:03,095
Kako zelite da platite
sve ovo?

339
00:34:03,935 --> 00:34:06,814
OK... Wayne.

340
00:34:07,695 --> 00:34:10,035
Silas!

341
00:34:12,375 --> 00:34:15,255
Na medenom mesecu smo.

342
00:34:22,095 --> 00:34:24,975
Ovuda.

343
00:34:25,174 --> 00:34:26,980
Kako mozemo da
priustimo sve ovo?

344
00:34:27,015 --> 00:34:29,894
Nisam uracunala u budzet
kristalne lustere i olimpijske
bazene.

345
00:34:30,894 --> 00:34:33,775
Zdravo.

346
00:34:33,895 --> 00:34:36,775
Zdravo. Svidja mi se vase
mesto. - Hvala. Ponecu vase
stvari.

347
00:34:36,975 --> 00:34:39,854
Oh, hvala.

348
00:34:42,655 --> 00:34:45,534
U redu.
Stigli smo.

349
00:34:45,614 --> 00:34:46,935
Apartman za mladence.

350
00:34:46,970 --> 00:34:49,814
Oh, boze!

351
00:34:51,535 --> 00:34:54,254
Mozda treba da pustimo malo
svezeg vazduha unutra.

352
00:34:54,289 --> 00:34:57,135
Da.
- Ovo ce biti zabavno, Tigre!

353
00:34:58,214 --> 00:35:01,094
Ako vam nesto zatreba, ne
oklevajte da pozovete recepciju.

354
00:35:01,655 --> 00:35:02,814
Hvala.
- Oni ce poslati nekoga.

355
00:35:02,849 --> 00:35:04,014
Zdravo, Leslie!
- Zdravo!

356
00:35:04,049 --> 00:35:06,894
Hvala!

357
00:35:15,374 --> 00:35:18,254
Moram da se istusiram.
- Ponovo?

358
00:35:19,374 --> 00:35:21,294
Da li bi voleo da ti se
pridruzim, Tigre?

359
00:35:21,329 --> 00:35:24,174
Ne!

360
00:35:46,654 --> 00:35:49,533
Oh, sranje.

361
00:35:53,013 --> 00:35:55,894
Camille?

362
00:36:07,493 --> 00:36:09,773
Camille!
Doneo sam ti ogrtac.

363
00:36:09,808 --> 00:36:11,298
Dobro mi je ovde, hvala.

364
00:36:11,333 --> 00:36:13,553
Hajde. Dovoljno si
bila unutra.

365
00:36:13,588 --> 00:36:15,773
Mogao bi i ti da udjes
ovde, Tigre.

366
00:36:15,808 --> 00:36:18,653
Ne.
Hajde.

367
00:36:21,733 --> 00:36:24,614
Tigre, zasto si tako
fin prema meni?

368
00:36:26,053 --> 00:36:28,933
Mislim, zahvalna sam ti. Ali
zelim da znam, jel' nesto nije
u redu?

369
00:36:29,893 --> 00:36:32,253
Ne bi mi verovala.

370
00:36:32,288 --> 00:36:35,133
Pa, iskusaj me.

371
00:36:42,893 --> 00:36:45,773
Ti si mrtva.

372
00:36:55,173 --> 00:36:58,052
Oh, boze!
Tigre, vidi!

373
00:37:00,173 --> 00:37:02,252
Hajde!
- Videla si plavog konja?

374
00:37:02,287 --> 00:37:04,333
Da. Mislim da je otisao
ovim putem.

375
00:37:04,653 --> 00:37:07,532
Zvuci ludo, ali videla sam
ovog konja i ranije.

376
00:37:08,692 --> 00:37:11,097
Pogledaj...

377
00:37:11,132 --> 00:37:14,013
Oh, boze, je li ovo
stvarno?

378
00:37:20,092 --> 00:37:22,057
Pa...

379
00:37:22,092 --> 00:37:24,498
Vidi sta nam je konj
dovukao.

380
00:37:24,533 --> 00:37:27,712
Nadao sam se da cemo
se videti ponovo.

381
00:37:29,292 --> 00:37:31,777
Mislio sam da cete stici
do vodopada do sada.

382
00:37:31,812 --> 00:37:34,692
Skrenuli smo pogresno par puta,
ali nas je Tigar vratio na put.

383
00:37:34,732 --> 00:37:37,097
Jel' tako, Tigre?

384
00:37:37,132 --> 00:37:39,577
Zasto bi... Obojio konja?

385
00:37:39,612 --> 00:37:42,492
Pa, sve je pocelo sa snom.

386
00:37:44,812 --> 00:37:48,191
Ali reci cu vam, zubi mu sigurno
izgledaju svetlije, zar ne?

387
00:37:49,772 --> 00:37:52,651
Naravno.
- Nije bas snazna.

388
00:37:53,932 --> 00:37:56,811
Pa, to je Maggie.
Pricao sam joj o tebi.

389
00:37:57,811 --> 00:38:00,137
Ne secas se tog dela?
- Ne.

390
00:38:00,172 --> 00:38:03,052
Pa, Maggie te poznaje.
Ispricao sam joj sve o tebi.

391
00:38:06,251 --> 00:38:09,132
Jel' tako, Maggie?
Jesam li ti ispricao?

392
00:38:11,531 --> 00:38:14,172
Maggie se dopadas.

393
00:38:14,207 --> 00:38:16,811
I meni se dopada Maggie.

394
00:38:17,772 --> 00:38:20,651
Tigre, pozeleneo si.

395
00:38:21,771 --> 00:38:23,272
Trebalo je da vas upozorim.

396
00:38:23,307 --> 00:38:24,736
Maggie je bolesna u
poslednje vreme.

397
00:38:24,771 --> 00:38:27,652
Eksperimentisao sam sa
specijalnom ishranom.

398
00:38:28,652 --> 00:38:31,531
Volim da probam nove
recepte.

399
00:38:32,332 --> 00:38:35,211
Jedva da mogu da pomirisem
nesto. Mislim da sam se navikao
na to.

400
00:38:36,531 --> 00:38:38,291
To ti je potrebno u ovom
poslu.

401
00:38:38,326 --> 00:38:39,811
U kaubojskom poslu?

402
00:38:39,846 --> 00:38:41,696
Ne, gospodjo.

403
00:38:41,731 --> 00:38:44,611
Kaubojski posao je
mrtav i nestao.

404
00:38:44,651 --> 00:38:47,531
Ovo je... Show business.

405
00:38:48,451 --> 00:38:51,331
Show business...

406
00:38:53,051 --> 00:38:56,890
Znas, Maggie je najpametniji
konj koga sam ikada upoznao.

407
00:38:57,491 --> 00:39:00,371
Jednog dana, samo je
odlutala i pronasla mene.

408
00:39:01,931 --> 00:39:03,456
Ne znam zasto.

409
00:39:03,491 --> 00:39:06,370
Ali znao sam da mora da
postoji razlog za to.

410
00:39:06,611 --> 00:39:09,491
Mogao sam to da joj
vidim u ocima.

411
00:39:10,131 --> 00:39:13,311
I od tada, trudim se da
je odrzim u zivotu.

412
00:39:14,851 --> 00:39:17,731
Znate, nisam ja jedan od
onih kauboja Novog doba,

413
00:39:20,010 --> 00:39:22,891
ali verujem u sudbinu.

414
00:39:23,091 --> 00:39:25,970
To je predivno.

415
00:39:28,171 --> 00:39:31,050
Silas, zar to nije najsladja
stvar koju si ikada cuo?

416
00:39:32,811 --> 00:39:35,210
Blizi se kraj za Maggie.

417
00:39:35,245 --> 00:39:36,656
Znam to.

418
00:39:36,691 --> 00:39:41,475
Pa, Roy Rogers je sacuvao
Trigger-a, kada je ovaj umro.

419
00:39:43,050 --> 00:39:45,931
Ali to je prica koju sam
ja cuo.

420
00:39:46,651 --> 00:39:47,815
Osecate li neki miris?

421
00:39:47,850 --> 00:39:50,250
Ne mogu da namirisem
nista osim konja.

422
00:39:50,285 --> 00:39:52,187
Silas, osecas li to?

423
00:39:52,222 --> 00:39:54,090
Da!
- Cudno je.

424
00:39:54,125 --> 00:39:56,211
Pitam se sta je to.

425
00:39:56,246 --> 00:39:57,695
Ti si.

426
00:39:57,730 --> 00:40:00,611
Silas Parker, ja ne smrdim!

427
00:40:03,090 --> 00:40:05,571
Zar ne?

428
00:40:05,606 --> 00:40:08,050
Da.

429
00:40:10,690 --> 00:40:13,570
Kuda ces?
- Ti ostani.

430
00:40:15,450 --> 00:40:18,330
Ocigledno je da ja
moram da odem.

431
00:40:21,490 --> 00:40:24,329
Pa, nije smrdela.

432
00:40:24,364 --> 00:40:27,135
Koliko?

433
00:40:27,170 --> 00:40:30,050
Primljeno.
Odmah stizemo.

434
00:40:30,970 --> 00:40:32,935
Mark!

435
00:40:32,970 --> 00:40:35,850
Zaustavicu tog kretena.
- Cekaj malo.

436
00:40:35,885 --> 00:40:37,255
To nam nece biti potrebno.

437
00:40:37,290 --> 00:40:38,974
Porodica koju je opljackao

438
00:40:39,009 --> 00:40:40,935
kaze da je non-stop pricao
kako je ubio nekoga.

439
00:40:40,970 --> 00:40:43,169
Trazimo prekrsioca uslovne,
koji je postao pljackas

440
00:40:43,204 --> 00:40:44,815
i moguce da je izvrsio
ubistvo.

441
00:40:44,850 --> 00:40:47,569
To je znak za opasnost. - On
cak nije sposoban za ubistvo.

442
00:40:47,604 --> 00:40:50,215
Silas krade stvari.
Male stvari.

443
00:40:50,250 --> 00:40:52,969
Jednom je ukrao mikrotalasnu
za majcin rodjendan.

444
00:40:53,004 --> 00:40:54,054
Znas, to je nekako slatko.

445
00:40:54,089 --> 00:40:55,655
Vidi, ja znam tog decka.

446
00:40:55,690 --> 00:40:58,569
Duboko u sebi, on je
pristojan momak.

447
00:40:58,729 --> 00:41:01,209
I zato si mu dozvolio da
prekrsi uslovnu?

448
00:41:01,244 --> 00:41:03,689
Zato sto duboko u sebi,
nije bio na uslovnoj?

449
00:41:04,169 --> 00:41:07,049
Ma daj! To je njihov medeni
mesec. Uostalom, ti ne poznajes
Camille.

450
00:41:07,369 --> 00:41:09,735
Ona uvek dobije ono
sto hoce.

451
00:41:09,770 --> 00:41:12,649
Zelela je njega,
skoro ceo zivot.

452
00:41:14,169 --> 00:41:16,769
Pa, nasao samo ovo u
polju kukuruza, juce.

453
00:41:16,804 --> 00:41:19,334
Blizu mesta nesrece.

454
00:41:19,369 --> 00:41:21,454
Izgleda da je bio prilicno
pripremljen.

455
00:41:21,489 --> 00:41:24,329
Ovo im je novac za medeni
mesec. - Oni nisu na medenom
mesecu.

456
00:41:24,364 --> 00:41:27,209
Beze prema granici!

457
00:41:31,169 --> 00:41:34,049
Hej, razumem da ti je
ona necaka.

458
00:41:35,049 --> 00:41:36,614
Mozes da nam se prikljucis.

459
00:41:36,649 --> 00:41:39,929
Ali svidelo ti se to ili ne, ovo
je sada moj medeni mesec.

460
00:41:44,809 --> 00:41:47,688
Gospodja je izgleda malo
iscrpljena.

461
00:41:50,289 --> 00:41:51,893
Ona je mrtva.

462
00:41:51,928 --> 00:41:54,809
Oh, da. Da.
Znam na sta mislis.

463
00:41:56,168 --> 00:41:59,049
Kada ne odspavam dobro, jedva
mogu da zapocnem sledeci dan.

464
00:41:59,249 --> 00:42:02,128
Ne, ona nije umorna.
Ona je mrtva.

465
00:42:07,608 --> 00:42:10,488
U kom smislu?

466
00:42:11,768 --> 00:42:14,648
Truli, raspada se.

467
00:42:15,688 --> 00:42:18,569
Svakim minutom sve je gore.

468
00:42:20,328 --> 00:42:24,309
Ne izgleda previse uznemireno
zbog toga. - Ona ne zna.

469
00:42:26,088 --> 00:42:28,968
Mislim, kako da kazes
nekome da je mrtav?

470
00:42:32,884 --> 00:42:35,528
Tacno tako.

471
00:43:19,042 --> 00:43:20,244
Bob!

472
00:43:20,279 --> 00:43:21,447
Bob?

473
00:43:27,848 --> 00:43:30,727
Imam 10 galona formaldehida.
Kreci!

474
00:43:37,607 --> 00:43:40,407
Ne mogu da verujem da
sam uradio to.

475
00:43:40,442 --> 00:43:41,693
To je bilo odlicno, Bob.

476
00:43:41,728 --> 00:43:44,607
Unistavanje privatne imovine.
Osecam se kao odmetnik.

477
00:43:54,062 --> 00:43:55,487
Bob! Bob! Bob!

478
00:43:55,522 --> 00:43:57,212
Bob!

479
00:43:57,247 --> 00:44:00,127
Sacekaj! Sacekaj!
Isuse!

480
00:44:00,326 --> 00:44:02,972
Hajde!

481
00:44:03,007 --> 00:44:04,387
Krenimo, druze.
- Da.

482
00:44:08,967 --> 00:44:11,687
Znam da nije moja stvar,

483
00:44:11,722 --> 00:44:14,406
ali sta ces joj uciniti?

484
00:44:16,887 --> 00:44:19,766
Samo cu je ocistiti,
reci joj istinu.

485
00:44:20,807 --> 00:44:23,686
Formaldehid ce otkloniti smrad.

486
00:44:23,721 --> 00:44:25,807
Kako ces joj saopstiti to?

487
00:44:25,842 --> 00:44:28,686
Ne znam.

488
00:44:28,766 --> 00:44:31,647
Moja zena obicno odradi
razgovor.

489
00:44:33,166 --> 00:44:36,047
Vi ste stvarno neobican par.

490
00:44:38,406 --> 00:44:40,647
Da.

491
00:44:41,647 --> 00:44:44,526
Kuci sam.

492
00:44:50,086 --> 00:44:52,646
Camille?

493
00:44:52,681 --> 00:44:55,207
Silas...

494
00:44:57,286 --> 00:44:59,571
Camille?

495
00:44:59,606 --> 00:45:01,606
Sta nije u redu?

496
00:45:06,486 --> 00:45:09,046
Nemoj, Silas. Samo nemoj!
- U redu je.

497
00:45:09,081 --> 00:45:11,926
Nemoj, Silas!
Ne gledaj me!

498
00:45:12,406 --> 00:45:15,286
U redu je.

499
00:45:18,885 --> 00:45:21,766
Sta mi se desava?

500
00:45:23,046 --> 00:45:25,926
Ne razumem.

501
00:45:26,566 --> 00:45:29,446
Svi mogu da vide.
Izgledam uzasno.

502
00:45:32,805 --> 00:45:35,686
Zasto se ovo desava?

503
00:45:37,605 --> 00:45:40,486
Mislim da si mrtva.

504
00:45:41,006 --> 00:45:43,885
Sta?

505
00:45:44,806 --> 00:45:47,685
Mislim da si mrtva.

506
00:45:48,965 --> 00:45:51,845
To nije moguce.

507
00:45:55,485 --> 00:45:58,365
Kako moze da bude to?
- Ne znam.

508
00:45:58,400 --> 00:46:01,245
To nema nikakvog smisla.

509
00:46:04,326 --> 00:46:07,130
Dodji ovamo.

510
00:46:07,165 --> 00:46:10,045
Ali, Tigre, ovo je nas
medeni mesec.

511
00:46:13,005 --> 00:46:15,885
Doneo sam ti nesto.

512
00:46:21,685 --> 00:46:24,565
Crvena je.

513
00:46:24,685 --> 00:46:27,565
Da.
Crvena.

514
00:46:33,725 --> 00:46:35,810
Da.

515
00:46:35,845 --> 00:46:38,725
Ne gledaj me.
Stidljiv sam.

516
00:46:39,525 --> 00:46:41,444
Rekao sam da me ne
gledas!

517
00:46:48,285 --> 00:46:50,744
Sta to radis?

518
00:46:50,779 --> 00:46:53,205
Samo se glupiram.

519
00:46:54,845 --> 00:46:57,724
Da li ti se dopada?

520
00:46:58,005 --> 00:47:00,884
To je najlepsa stvar koju
sam ikada videla.

521
00:47:02,644 --> 00:47:03,885
Stvarno tako mislis?

522
00:47:03,920 --> 00:47:06,369
Da.

523
00:47:06,404 --> 00:47:09,284
Hvala ti, Tigre.

524
00:47:16,164 --> 00:47:19,044
Sta cemo da radimo,
Silas?

525
00:47:21,724 --> 00:47:24,604
Samo mi reci da cu da
budem u redu.

526
00:47:27,484 --> 00:47:30,324
Nisam stvarno mrtva.

527
00:47:30,359 --> 00:47:33,169
U redu?

528
00:47:33,204 --> 00:47:35,169
U redu.

529
00:47:35,204 --> 00:47:38,084
I uspecemo da stignemo
do vodopada.

530
00:47:39,364 --> 00:47:42,244
Necemo sada da stanemo,
nikako.

531
00:47:44,004 --> 00:47:46,368
Mozemo da uspemo.

532
00:47:46,403 --> 00:47:48,489
Makar mi to bilo poslednje
sto cu da uradim, Camille,

533
00:47:48,524 --> 00:47:51,403
obecavam ti, odvescu te
na Nijagarine vodopade.

534
00:48:00,523 --> 00:48:03,404
Prokleti djevrek je star
dve nedelje.

535
00:48:04,443 --> 00:48:07,324
Planirala je ceo svoj raspored,
kada je on imao sastanak sa
uslovnom komisijom,

536
00:48:07,724 --> 00:48:10,603
samo da bi mogla da baci
pogled na njega u mojoj
kancelariji.

537
00:48:11,163 --> 00:48:14,043
Niste je odgovorili od ovoga?
- Pokusao sam.

538
00:48:14,723 --> 00:48:18,800
Pokazao sam joj snimke sigurnosne
kamere, iz noci kada smo ga pokupili
kod B & A-a.

539
00:48:19,483 --> 00:48:22,864
Sve o cemu je ona govorila
je da je izgledao slatko u
dzemperu.

540
00:48:23,323 --> 00:48:26,204
Kako mozete da stanete
na put necem takvom?

541
00:48:27,204 --> 00:48:30,083
Ja bih upucao momka.

542
00:48:41,323 --> 00:48:44,123
Privescemo ga samo na
ispitivanje, zar ne?

543
00:48:44,158 --> 00:48:45,923
Necemo da povredimo nikoga?

544
00:48:45,958 --> 00:48:47,248
Pa, to zavisi od njega.

545
00:48:47,283 --> 00:48:50,163
Ali za slucaj da stvari postanu
gadne, ti ostajes ovde,

546
00:48:50,682 --> 00:48:53,563
i ne dolazis tamo dok
ne vidim na cemu smo.

547
00:48:55,202 --> 00:48:57,923
To je moja necaka.
Ma hajde!

548
00:48:57,958 --> 00:49:00,643
Ostani.
I ti ostani sa njim.

549
00:49:08,603 --> 00:49:10,087
Camille?

550
00:49:10,122 --> 00:49:13,003
Jesi li u redu?
- Nikad bolje, Tigre.

551
00:49:15,202 --> 00:49:18,082
Danas je novi dan.

552
00:49:18,442 --> 00:49:21,323
Da.

553
00:49:22,602 --> 00:49:24,802
Da, gospodine, ovde su.

554
00:49:25,483 --> 00:49:26,368
Perimetar obezbedjen?

555
00:49:26,403 --> 00:49:27,642
Perimetar obezdjen, da.

556
00:49:27,677 --> 00:49:28,442
Idem okolo.

557
00:49:28,477 --> 00:49:29,602
U redu, momci, ulazimo.

558
00:49:29,637 --> 00:49:31,140
Pokrivam izlaze!

559
00:49:31,175 --> 00:49:32,642
U redu, imam ih!

560
00:49:33,442 --> 00:49:34,402
Bellman!

561
00:49:34,963 --> 00:49:35,923
Hej! Hej!
- Sta je?

562
00:49:41,722 --> 00:49:43,567
Bellman!

563
00:49:43,602 --> 00:49:45,802
Dobro, mozes li da skocis?
- Oh, boze!

564
00:49:45,837 --> 00:49:48,002
Tigre, sta cemo sa nasim
stvarima? - Imam ih ovde.

565
00:49:48,037 --> 00:49:50,882
Ne mogu da skocim dole!
Ne mogu! Tigre, ne mogu.

566
00:49:52,642 --> 00:49:55,407
Dobro.
Dobro, onda.

567
00:49:55,442 --> 00:49:57,042
Moraces da uradis
nesto drugo, u redu?

568
00:49:57,077 --> 00:49:58,527
U redu.

569
00:49:58,562 --> 00:50:00,762
Oh, imam kljuc.

570
00:50:10,842 --> 00:50:13,721
Policija!
Stoj!

571
00:50:14,041 --> 00:50:16,922
Oh, Isuse.
Proverite sobu.

572
00:50:20,802 --> 00:50:23,681
Ledena kao kamen.

573
00:50:32,881 --> 00:50:35,762
Posaljite islednika.
Ona je mrtva.

574
00:50:49,162 --> 00:50:52,041
Balkon je cist!

575
00:51:06,081 --> 00:51:08,961
Neka ideja o ovim mrljama?

576
00:51:10,721 --> 00:51:13,601
Mislim da je formaldehid.

577
00:51:14,121 --> 00:51:17,001
Bolesno kopile.

578
00:51:33,081 --> 00:51:35,960
Nikada se ne naviknes na
ovakve stvari.

579
00:51:36,240 --> 00:51:38,886
Mi smo imuni na to,
gospodjo.

580
00:51:38,921 --> 00:51:41,800
Kada ste policajac, bili ste
na tim mracnim mestima.

581
00:51:44,681 --> 00:51:47,521
Videli ste zlo koje vreba
u ljudskom srcu.

582
00:51:51,440 --> 00:51:53,881
Ne, stani, molim te!

583
00:51:58,356 --> 00:52:01,280
Stani!

584
00:52:36,600 --> 00:52:38,920
Nema potrebe da lazemo,
znas na sta mislim?

585
00:52:38,955 --> 00:52:39,965
Svi pravimo greske.

586
00:52:40,000 --> 00:52:42,880
Sefe, kunem se Bogom,
kinula je u liftu.

587
00:52:43,680 --> 00:52:48,150
Kada sam je poslednji put
video, Riley, bila je mrtva i
nije disala.

588
00:52:49,639 --> 00:52:51,360
Ali ti si je video da kija?

589
00:52:51,395 --> 00:52:54,239
Da.

590
00:52:55,079 --> 00:52:57,960
Sta je onda uradila,
pocela da leti po sobi?

591
00:52:58,560 --> 00:53:01,440
Uh, ne, ustvari, on
je strcao niz hodnik.

592
00:53:09,319 --> 00:53:12,200
Isuse, Tigre, ovo je trebalo
da bude nas novi zivot.

593
00:53:12,639 --> 00:53:14,324
Bez problema sa vlastima.

594
00:53:14,359 --> 00:53:17,239
A evo mene, tvoje nove zene,
uvalila sam te u nevolju.

595
00:53:24,679 --> 00:53:27,559
U tvojoj majici je rupa.
- Sta?

596
00:53:28,479 --> 00:53:31,359
Oh, boze.
Volim ovu majicu.

597
00:53:31,639 --> 00:53:34,519
Ovo je bila nasa majica kupljena
za zabavu. Ti si mi je kupio.

598
00:53:36,359 --> 00:53:38,164
Znas sta je u pitanju?

599
00:53:38,199 --> 00:53:41,079
Znala sam - to je zbog
pirinca.

600
00:53:41,359 --> 00:53:43,084
Rekla sam im da je trebalo da
imamo pirinac na vencanju.

601
00:53:43,119 --> 00:53:45,999
Rekla sam da nije vencanje
bez pirinca. To je los znak.

602
00:53:46,879 --> 00:53:49,758
Jos jedna rupa je ovde.
Daj da vidim.

603
00:53:50,559 --> 00:53:53,439
Sranje!

604
00:53:55,839 --> 00:53:58,199
To je rupa od metka.
- Osecam se dobro.

605
00:53:58,234 --> 00:53:59,603
Ne zelim da pricamo
o tome.

606
00:53:59,638 --> 00:54:02,519
Nista mi nije sa...
Znas...

607
00:54:02,559 --> 00:54:05,199
Malecka rupa u mom
ramenu.

608
00:54:05,234 --> 00:54:07,838
Dve rupe.
- Nista mi nije.

609
00:54:11,399 --> 00:54:13,718
Znas sta?
Svidja mi se crvena kosa.

610
00:54:13,753 --> 00:54:15,284
Stvarno.

611
00:54:15,319 --> 00:54:18,198
Kada mi izraste kosa, mislim
da cu je obojiti ovako.

612
00:54:19,158 --> 00:54:21,723
To je fino.

613
00:54:39,439 --> 00:54:42,203
Hej...

614
00:54:42,238 --> 00:54:44,638
Hej, Robert.
- Iris.

615
00:54:44,673 --> 00:54:47,038
Hoces li da ostanes
ovoga puta?

616
00:54:47,073 --> 00:54:49,358
Zavisi.

617
00:54:54,118 --> 00:54:56,518
Cime hranis ove konje?

618
00:54:56,553 --> 00:54:59,398
Pa...

619
00:55:02,798 --> 00:55:05,678
Zdravo.

620
00:55:06,718 --> 00:55:09,598
Zdravo.
Imas slepe putnike.

621
00:55:10,078 --> 00:55:12,457
Oh, mi smo mladenci.

622
00:55:12,492 --> 00:55:14,838
Znate kako je.

623
00:55:20,998 --> 00:55:23,398
Nisam navikao na ovakve
stvari -

624
00:55:23,433 --> 00:55:25,655
pljacke i provale,

625
00:55:25,690 --> 00:55:27,842
kradju, kradju tela...

626
00:55:27,877 --> 00:55:30,717
To je za mladice.

627
00:55:30,752 --> 00:55:33,523
Ja sam star covek, Silas.

628
00:55:33,558 --> 00:55:35,677
Nisam nimalo spavao
prosle noci.

629
00:55:35,712 --> 00:55:37,482
Samo nas odvedi do
granice.

630
00:55:37,517 --> 00:55:40,397
Onda mozes da zaboravis
da si nas poznavao.

631
00:55:41,077 --> 00:55:43,958
Izvini, momce.
Nisam ja dobar za vas.

632
00:55:47,477 --> 00:55:49,882
Ili za bilo koga.

633
00:55:49,917 --> 00:55:52,797
Pa, poznajem Robert-a
vec 15 godina.

634
00:55:53,957 --> 00:55:56,837
Uvek je imao ovog konja.

635
00:55:57,117 --> 00:56:00,897
Znam da se dobro brine o
Maggie, ali pogledaj ove plikove.

636
00:56:01,957 --> 00:56:04,317
Poceces da se ljustis
kao stara boja.

637
00:56:04,352 --> 00:56:07,197
Ne bi trebalo da si ziva
do sada.

638
00:56:07,396 --> 00:56:09,922
Mozda jos uvek nije
spremna da ode.

639
00:56:09,957 --> 00:56:12,837
Niko nije spreman za to,
zar ne?

640
00:56:14,997 --> 00:56:17,842
Znas, mlada i lepa nevesta
kao ti

641
00:56:17,877 --> 00:56:20,757
ne treba da ide u toj staroj,
prljavoj, pocepanoj suknji.

642
00:56:21,276 --> 00:56:23,997
Znam. Nekako sam
izgubila sve stvari usput.

643
00:56:24,032 --> 00:56:26,561
Volis li odecu za rodeo?

644
00:56:26,596 --> 00:56:29,477
Dame i gospodo,
decaci i devojcice,

645
00:56:30,516 --> 00:56:32,922
ovo su konji razlicitih boja.

646
00:56:32,957 --> 00:56:38,700
Ovde jahanje nikada ne
prestaje. Ovde je zivot vecan.

647
00:56:39,676 --> 00:56:42,157
Ostani na njemu,
devojcice.

648
00:56:42,192 --> 00:56:44,636
Zar Silas nije sladak
dok pomaze?

649
00:56:47,849 --> 00:56:49,000
Silas, vidi.

650
00:56:49,550 --> 00:56:51,600
"Ubica na drumu".

651
00:56:51,997 --> 00:56:54,556
To je tako smesno, Tigre.
Ti nisi ubio nikoga.

652
00:56:54,591 --> 00:56:56,333
Zasto bi rekli to?

653
00:56:56,368 --> 00:56:58,041
Sta cemo da radimo?

654
00:56:58,076 --> 00:57:00,236
Otici cemo odavde.
- Mislim, posle toga.

655
00:57:00,271 --> 00:57:03,116
Sta ce se desiti kada budemo
hteli da se vratimo kuci?

656
00:57:03,796 --> 00:57:06,677
Ja se ne vracam kuci.

657
00:57:07,197 --> 00:57:10,076
U redu.

658
00:57:14,876 --> 00:57:17,756
Silas?

659
00:57:17,956 --> 00:57:20,836
Covece, mozes li samo da
nas odvedes do vodopada?

660
00:57:24,716 --> 00:57:27,596
Ne idete na ples?

661
00:57:27,836 --> 00:57:29,241
Ja ne plesem.

662
00:57:29,276 --> 00:57:32,156
Nikada nisi plesao sa
svojom zenom?

663
00:57:34,556 --> 00:57:37,436
Ona ne moze da
ceka vecno.

664
00:57:49,635 --> 00:57:52,516
Ne izgleda dobro,
Bob-e.

665
00:57:54,395 --> 00:57:57,276
Pa, jos je ziva, jos sutira.

666
00:57:57,476 --> 00:57:59,475
Samo srecan konj moze
to da kaze,

667
00:57:59,510 --> 00:58:02,356
cak i ako ne moze
stvarno da kaze.

668
00:58:03,075 --> 00:58:05,916
Izgleda kao da joj
treba malo nege.

669
00:58:10,476 --> 00:58:12,160
Bob?

670
00:58:12,195 --> 00:58:15,075
Mogu li da ti zatrazim
cudnu uslugu?

671
00:58:18,395 --> 00:58:20,796
Jarko narandzasta!

672
00:58:20,831 --> 00:58:23,195
Izgleda preplanulo!

673
00:58:23,675 --> 00:58:26,555
Sta je to?

674
00:58:27,035 --> 00:58:29,916
Samo ignorisi taj deo.
Mozes da ofarbas iznad toga.

675
00:58:37,795 --> 00:58:40,315
Camille?

676
00:58:40,350 --> 00:58:42,835
Izadji.

677
00:59:02,509 --> 00:59:04,199
Vidis?

678
00:59:04,234 --> 00:59:07,114
Dobar si plesac,
Tigre.

679
00:59:07,434 --> 00:59:10,200
Imam osecaj kao da me
svi gledaju.

